<Base title="License — Saralcare Ambulance Directory">
  <h2 style="margin-top:0">License</h2>

  <p>The Saralcare Ambulance Directory uses three separate licenses for three layers of the project:</p>

  <div class="card">
    <h3 style="margin-top:0">Data — CC BY-NC-SA 4.0</h3>
    <p>
      The structured ambulance + hospital data is licensed under
      <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Free for: individuals, families, doctors, hospitals (for patient care), journalists, researchers, NGOs, civic-tech projects, government and govt-contracted EMS.
    </p>
    <p>
      Requires a separate bilateral license for: any for-profit product, app, API, or service. Email <a href="mailto:ashwinsk@saralcare.com?subject=%5BLICENSE+REQUEST%5D">ashwinsk@saralcare.com</a>. There is no public price list and no self-serve.
    </p>
    <p>Attribution required for all uses. See the <a href="https://github.com/Ashwask/SaralcareAmbulanceservices/blob/main/LICENSE-FAQ.md"><code>LICENSE-FAQ.md</code></a> for worked examples.</p>
