      Commercial republication is allowed for the writing — only the structured data has the non-commercial clause.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h3>Attribution format</h3>
  <pre style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 6px; overflow-x: auto;">Source: Saralcare ambulance directory project
(https://ambulance.saralcare.com), CC BY-NC-SA 4.0.</pre>

  <h3>Full license texts</h3>
